name: Vision Board Template
description:
Start the next year on the right track by using this easy-to-edit vision board template to set the goals you hope to accomplish next year.


Customize each block

Download the Unsplash plugin to pick a photo that describes each of your goals.


Print your template

After taking some time to add the title for each of your goals, print your art board and put it in a place that you see every day!


Enjoy it.


Made with love by Lilibeth Bustos Linares
